---
title: Autumnal Butternut and Bacon Mac and Cheese with a Crispy Sage Crumb
description: Mac and cheese is a crowd-pleasing American dish with a deliciously cheesy sauce. The butternut squash and sage crumb here makes it even better, taking it from a regular mac and cheese to one that's perfect for autumn.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R43_W38_UK_V14002-21_Main_low_2-9a1e0343.jpg
